1
00:00:06,080 --> 00:00:07,080
What?

2
00:00:08,250 --> 00:00:09,670
I'm sorry.

3
00:00:10,170 --> 00:00:12,040
I couldn't help myself.

4
00:00:14,380 --> 00:00:15,830
I'm sorry.

5
00:00:16,170 --> 00:00:17,170
What was that!

6
00:00:17,920 --> 00:00:19,040
What do you call that?

7
00:00:20,290 --> 00:00:21,290
A kiss?

8
00:00:21,710 --> 00:00:22,710
Why?

9
00:00:23,830 --> 00:00:24,830
Why?

10
00:00:24,920 --> 00:00:25,920
Because, Reika-san...

11
00:00:26,420 --> 00:00:27,130
You kept bringing up

12
00:00:27,210 --> 00:00:28,420
the president's name.

13
00:00:28,420 --> 00:00:29,420
So what?

14
00:00:30,330 --> 00:00:31,330
I got jealous.

15
00:00:32,290 --> 00:00:33,290
Because I was jealous...

16
00:00:35,290 --> 00:00:36,960
My feelings for you
just overflowed.

17
00:00:40,040 --> 00:00:41,920
How I feel about you...

18
00:00:42,330 --> 00:00:44,170
You can't possibly not know, can you?

19
00:00:44,420 --> 00:00:45,420
Right.

20
00:00:45,790 --> 00:00:47,540
I will never forgive you.

21
00:00:47,670 --> 00:00:48,330
I know.

22
00:00:48,330 --> 00:00:50,670
I hate you more than anyone.

23
00:00:51,290 --> 00:00:52,040
I know.

24
00:00:52,290 --> 00:00:53,290
Then why!

25
00:00:54,290 --> 00:00:55,380
I'm sorry.

26
00:00:56,920 --> 00:00:57,920
I swear I will

27
00:00:58,960 --> 00:00:59,830
drag you down

28
00:00:59,830 --> 00:01:00,960
into an even deeper hell.

29
00:01:01,580 --> 00:01:02,330
I'll make you suffer

30
00:01:02,330 --> 00:01:04,630
the same way you made me.

31
00:01:06,290 --> 00:01:07,630
Hate me.

32
00:01:07,960 --> 00:01:09,960
I want you to hate me.

33
00:01:10,880 --> 00:01:11,880
But...

34
00:01:12,290 --> 00:01:14,210
If you really hate me...

35
00:01:15,670 --> 00:01:16,580
then why are you

36
00:01:16,580 --> 00:01:18,000
still wearing that ring?
